title: HI-FASHION -- Special Pre-Release CD
description:
By special request HI-FASHION presents our "Pre-Release" CD, featuring many of the songs that will be included on the final version of our finished CD.

Hi-Fashion is:
Harry Billings, Christine Vreeland, Allen Newton, Ivy Kemper, and Cy Yates.
